descriptionHtml:
Hello,
This is a preset of Jocaste, a young imperial agent female, working for the imperial army.
I hope you like this preset.

[b]Step 1 - Requirements :[/b]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]RaceMenu by [b]Expired[/b]
[/url]
Step 2 - Mods recommended (for the same appearance) :

Body and face texture : [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url][/b]

Hair :[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c4kU-kdnf5U]Skyrim KS Hairdo Female Hair[/url] (Remove from the Nexus ?) > 0topgorgeous
Brows : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows by [b]Hello Santa[/b][/url] > 09
Eyes :  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49069/?]Improved Eyes Skyrim by [b]missjennabee[/b][/url] > EyesHumanGreen19
Lips : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips HD by [b]EcthelionOtW[/b][/url]
Make up : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE by [b]Diethardt[/b][/url]
ENB : I use the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/42957/?]Mistveil by [b]Modd3r[/b][/url][b] [/b]preset in my screenshoots. Other ENB are nice too.

NB : She has a beauty spot, but i don't remember from what mod it comes.

Step 3 - How to install

If you have RaceMenu version 3 or higher :
Copy the file Imperial_Jocaste.jslot here : Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
Go into showracemenu
Go on the preset tab
Hit F9 for load the preset. 
Choose the preset Imperial_Jocaste.jslot

If you have an ancient version of RaceMenu :
Copy the file 21.slot here : Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
Go into showracemenu
Set race to imperial and load the preset Slot 21 (Hit F9 to load the preset.)
I put size at 0.97 or 0.98.

Enjoy!

My other preset :

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61168/?]Roxanne preset for RaceMenu[/url] (Nord)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61553/?]Salma preset for RaceMenu[/url] (Redguard)
